OL,6,FThe Health Secretary has called for an
OL,7,Finvestigation into a major private
OL,8,Fcare company after an ITV News
OL,9,Finvestigation exposed serious neglect
OL,10,Fat care homes for disabled adults.
OL,12,FWes Streeting said the allegations
OL,13,Fagainst Lifeways were "extremely
OL,14,Fserious" and he would be speaking
OL,15,Furgently to the Care Quality
OL,16,FCommission who have the power to take
OL,17,Faction.
