OL,6,FSeveral families, as well as current
OL,7,Fand former staff members, told ITV
OL,8,FNews about "dangerous" understaffing,
OL,9,Flack of training and poor levels of
OL,10,Fcare at Lifeways residential and
OL,11,Fsupported living homes.
OL,13,FOne 23-year-old man requiring round-
OL,14,Fthe-clock care was filmed eating out
OL,15,Fof a bin in the middle of the night,
OL,16,Fwith no carer in sight. Another man
OL,17,Fwith Down's Syndrome was left with an
OL,18,Funtreated foot infection requiring
OL,19,Fhospital treatment.
