OL,6,FWe showed the footage from Connor's
OL,7,Fapartment to Coventry City Council's
OL,8,FDirector of Care, Health and Housing,
OL,9,FPete Fahy. He described it as
OL,10,F"appalling".
OL,12,F"That type of conduct, that sort of
OL,13,Fneglect is never acceptable," he said.
OL,15,F"We hope to never see that type of
OL,16,Fincident happen anywhere in the city
OL,17,Fever again. And we're really grateful
OL,18,Fthat when it does and people identify
OL,19,Fit, we take robust action and we put
OL,20,Fmeasures in place to safeguard the
OL,21,Findividual."
