OL,6,FHe has autism, and is non-verbal. He
OL,7,Fwas living at Grove Court, a Lifeways
OL,8,Fsupported living residence in Shepton
OL,9,FMallet, Somerset.
OL,11,FLast year, David's sister Lisa was on
OL,12,Fthe way to visit him at his home when
OL,13,Fshe saw him on the street outside -
OL,14,Falone, barefoot, with no carer in
OL,15,Fsight. David was supposed to receive
OL,16,F15 hours of one-to-one care a day, and
OL,17,Fcannot be alone in the community.
OL,19,F"He shouldn't be outside on his own,"
OL,20,FLisa told us.
